#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_collisionpolygon.rst:19
msgid ""
"Allows editing a collision polygon's vertices on a selected plane. Can "
"also set a depth perpendicular to that plane. This class is only "
"available in the editor. It will not appear in the scene tree at run-"
"time. Creates a :ref:`Shape <class_Shape>` for gameplay. Properties "
"modified during gameplay will have no effect."
msgstr ""

